# ============================================================
# s.suite / .gitignore
# This repo is a PORTABLE, GENERIC toolkit. Nothing project-
# specific, machine-specific, or proprietary should ever land
# here. The rules below are deliberately aggressive.
# ============================================================

# --- Secrets & credentials (never commit) ---
.env
.env.*
*.local
.credentials.json
.claude.json
**/credentials*
**/secrets*
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
id_rsa*
*.token

# --- Local / machine-specific Claude settings ---
# settings.local.json holds per-machine overrides and possible
# secrets. It must NEVER be committed.
settings.local.json
**/settings.local.json
global/settings.local.json

# --- Session-specific safety + context state ---
# These are produced at runtime in real repos, not here.
.claude/context/
.claude/session-state/
**/.freeze-boundary
**/current-session.md
*.session.md

# --- Backups created by install/sync scripts ---
*.bak
*.backup
backup-*/
.claude-backup-*/

# --- Local design / planning docs (not part of the portable toolkit) ---
# Specs and plans are working artifacts for building the toolkit, not
# something installed into ~/.claude. Keep them local.
docs/

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
